# Logs
# Scoped to a root-level logs/ dir — a bare `logs` also matched the
# src/panels/logs/ SOURCE directory, so the Logs panel never got committed
# (local builds worked, clones/CI broke on the missing module).
/logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
